Theme:Able to create Enterprise Applications
History:
Before EJB, Java Beanswere used  to create Enterprise Applications such as Web Applications
Although Java Beans were used to create UI components hence they couldnt provide services such as transaction management and security which are needed to create robust and secure eneterprise applications
The advent of EJB brought solution to this complication
EJB extends Java Components such as Web and Enterprise Components and provides services that helps in Enterprise Application Development
Enterprise applicatiopn:An application tthat a business would use to assist an organization basically in a Corporate World


